Serie A results

This is a collection of interactive (well, just a little bit) heatmaps showing all results of each club that played in Serie A from the 1986-87 season to the 2016-17 season. Put your cursor on a square to see the result of any specific game.
Step 1 - Data collection
I used Beautifulsoup to extract data from the website of the Lega Serie A and saved the data into a csv.
Step 2 - Data manipulation
I then organised the data into Pandas DataFrames and created a dictionary with a DataFrame for each club.
Step 3 - Data visualisation
Finally I used Bokeh to create the heatmaps and add the tooltip on hovering.

Please be patient, it may take about 30 seconds to load
